title: Nautilus missing from Ocean Week

embed.description: The sun is shining and the waves are up, which means the Australia Day and Waitangi Day long weekends are not far off! To celebrate we're issuing a challenge of aquatic proportions. If you can rally together as a community and contribute enough points during Ocean Week you will unlock rewards for everyone that participates.

body: {{champion:111}} Nautilus was confirmed to be in the first wave of champions, but for some reason instead of him we have {{champion:107}}  Rengar. Fix this please I was really looking forward to Nautilus jungle :( {{item:3070}}

replies.body: Fixed now, thanks again for reporting!
Thanks man :P. All I want now is for you and Mr Hawk to put on the tool belt and build it yourself.
WELL AIN'T IT A GOOD THING TO BE ABLE TO LOG INTO THE CLIENT, EH?
Thanks for the report, working on this right now.
